WEBVTT

00:01:39.519 --> 00:01:41.400
Look! That's the one who killed Lord Meng!

00:01:41.799 --> 00:01:42.640
Murderer!

00:01:42.799 --> 00:01:44.040
Lord Meng was a good official!

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:44.719
Exactly!

00:01:44.959 --> 00:01:46.359
Someone like him should go to hell!

00:01:46.719 --> 00:01:47.480
Kill him!

00:01:47.519 --> 00:01:48.159
Kill him!

00:01:55.760 --> 00:01:58.439
The Qutang Gorge roars through twelve rapids,

00:01:59.159 --> 00:02:01.760
A path treacherous since ancient times.

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:05.560
I lament that the human heart is unlike water,

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:09.560
For even on flat ground,

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:14.159
Sudden waves arise.

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:17.080
Hold the execution!

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:23.639
By order of the Dali Temple!

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.840
Bring the death row prisoner Ye Li for interrogation!

00:02:26.719 --> 00:02:27.479
Lord Hua.

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.360
This is the true culprit who killed Governor Lord Meng.

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:33.199
He is the one Lord Nine Thousand Years personally ordered beheaded.

00:02:36.439 --> 00:02:36.960
What?

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:39.360
The Emperor is bedridden.

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:41.400
Throughout the court,

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:43.479
Lord Nine Thousand Years calls the shots now.

00:02:53.639 --> 00:02:54.479
Release him.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:55.759
Release him!

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:56.560
Release him!

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:13.919
Let's go.

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:23.199
How could they just let him go?

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:24.680
Yeah, they just left like that?

00:03:36.919 --> 00:03:38.439
The Master of Baixiao Villa

00:03:38.800 --> 00:03:40.280
has been missing for over a month.

00:03:41.479 --> 00:03:43.080
The Governor responsible for this case

00:03:43.400 --> 00:03:44.400
was also suddenly killed.

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:46.360
Minister Yin,

00:03:47.439 --> 00:03:48.159
what is your view?

00:03:48.719 --> 00:03:49.400
Your Highness,

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:51.000
the Master of Baixiao Villa

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:53.479
has always been very close to Lord Nine Thousand Years.

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.719
His connections in court are also deeply entrenched.

00:03:57.680 --> 00:03:58.560
I believe

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:00.400
it is inconvenient to investigate this openly.

00:04:00.560 --> 00:04:01.919
It would be better to investigate secretly.

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:05.719
It seems Minister Yin already has a candidate.

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:08.879
Magistrate Hua Qiankun.

00:04:12.599 --> 00:04:13.319
Your Highness,

00:04:13.599 --> 00:04:14.960
Ye Li, the prime suspect in the Governor's murder case,

00:04:15.360 --> 00:04:17.120
left a letter written in blood before heading to the execution ground.

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:19.519
He is willing to help Dali Temple solve the Baixiao Villa case.

00:04:21.879 --> 00:04:23.560
However, he has a condition.

00:04:23.879 --> 00:04:25.519
If the Baixiao Villa case is solved,

00:04:26.519 --> 00:04:28.600
he asks Your Highness to retry his case.

00:04:41.839 --> 00:04:42.279
My Lord.

00:04:42.879 --> 00:04:43.560
The prisoner has been brought.

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:45.240
Master Kun,

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.319
the Lord has other urgent matters.

00:04:47.519 --> 00:04:48.639
He asked me to give this to you.

00:04:52.399 --> 00:04:54.360
The Summer Solstice brings the Baixiao Night,

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:56.920
All things renew as we await your arrival.

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.839
The Lord orders you two to attend the Baixiao Night Banquet together

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:01.279
to investigate the disappearance of the Villa Master.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.319
Those who get an invitation every year

00:05:05.120 --> 00:05:06.399
are either honored guests of the Villa

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:07.920
or have paid a heavy price.

00:05:08.920 --> 00:05:11.319
It seems Dali Temple is truly desperate to solve the case.

00:05:12.480 --> 00:05:14.920
But that Baixiao Villa is overly mysterious.

00:05:15.199 --> 00:05:17.240
Hidden in a dense forest in Wumei Valley,

00:05:17.639 --> 00:05:18.800
filled with poisonous miasma,

00:05:18.879 --> 00:05:20.279
where neither gods nor ghosts dare approach.

00:05:20.879 --> 00:05:21.560
Rest assured, Master Kun.

00:05:21.839 --> 00:05:23.160
This pill can neutralize the miasma poison.

00:05:47.319 --> 00:05:47.839
Who is it?

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:49.199
Get lost.

00:05:49.680 --> 00:05:50.399
What a killjoy.

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:00.360
Who's there?

00:06:15.319 --> 00:06:16.040
The Master...

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:55.879
Since the Master is missing,

00:06:56.399 --> 00:06:57.519
as for this year's business,

00:06:57.639 --> 00:06:58.519
how will they manage?

00:07:02.079 --> 00:07:03.120
Say, Lord Hua,

00:07:03.480 --> 00:07:04.720
I've been following you all this way.

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:06.040
How about

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:07.839
you help me unlock this?

00:07:08.519 --> 00:07:08.920
Look,

00:07:09.399 --> 00:07:10.480
my wrists are nearly rotting.

00:07:12.680 --> 00:07:14.800
Removing your wooden collar was already an act of mercy.

00:07:15.399 --> 00:07:15.959
As for this,

00:07:16.600 --> 00:07:17.519
don't even think about it.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:20.680
Lord Hua,

00:07:21.319 --> 00:07:23.079
I can't investigate the case wearing this.

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:25.480
And it looks bad if others see it.

00:07:29.879 --> 00:07:30.480
Hide it well.

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:44.759
We are here to attend a banquet.

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.319
The legendary Baixiao Villa.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:07.279
It's supposed to be magnificent,

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:09.040
but it's so deserted now.

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:11.680
Why is there a big rock placed here?

00:08:12.319 --> 00:08:13.480
Isn't the Night Banquet today?

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:15.120
I don't see any guests,

00:08:15.759 --> 00:08:17.360
and there's no banquet atmosphere.

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:23.959
He doesn't seem to speak.

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:31.959
All mysterious.

00:08:32.639 --> 00:08:33.759
It seems this Baixiao Villa

00:08:33.759 --> 00:08:34.759
is indeed not that simple.

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:55.200
She seems...

00:08:58.759 --> 00:08:59.600
At a time like this,

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.320
you're still in the mood to ogle girls?

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:02.639
Let's go.

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:43.639
Get down.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:45.759
Well, I didn't have a seat.

00:09:47.440 --> 00:09:48.799
The Villa Master has been missing for days.

00:09:49.279 --> 00:09:50.639
The discipline at Baixiao Villa

00:09:50.639 --> 00:09:52.039
has become increasingly lax.

00:09:53.320 --> 00:09:54.720
The Night Banquet is of such importance,

00:09:55.799 --> 00:09:57.600
yet they even invited people like this.

00:09:59.240 --> 00:10:01.360
Thank you, honored guests, for coming from afar.

00:10:02.159 --> 00:10:02.759
Young Mistress.

00:10:02.919 --> 00:10:03.879
Young Mistress! Young Mistress!

00:10:10.919 --> 00:10:14.600
I, Xu Qingqing, pay my respects to you all.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:17.320
Everyone, please take a seat.

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:18.679
Thank you, Young Mistress.

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:28.639
I presume you all know

00:10:29.039 --> 00:10:30.399
that my father has been missing for many days.

00:10:31.399 --> 00:10:33.879
The guards, servants, and stewards of the villa

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:35.279
have all been sent out by me

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:36.840
to search for my father's whereabouts.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:39.360
Now, my head maid, Xiaobai,

00:10:39.799 --> 00:10:41.039
is acting as the steward.

00:10:42.440 --> 00:10:43.919
If any honored guests need anything,

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:45.360
just ask her.

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:48.120
I've long heard the Villa Master

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.399
dotes on the Young Mistress.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:51.799
She hasn't left the house since childhood.

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:54.639
I've been friends with the Villa Master for years,

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:57.240
and tonight I finally get to meet you.

00:10:57.639 --> 00:10:58.919
I have been frail since childhood,

00:10:59.360 --> 00:11:00.519
and have always lived in the West Courtyard,

00:11:00.799 --> 00:11:01.720
never seeing outsiders.

00:11:02.519 --> 00:11:04.080
Now that my father is missing,

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:05.679
the Baixiao Villa Night Banquet

00:11:06.120 --> 00:11:07.360
is being hosted by me in his stead.

00:11:08.279 --> 00:11:09.720
If the hospitality is lacking in any way,

00:11:09.919 --> 00:11:11.159
I ask for your forgiveness.

00:11:11.679 --> 00:11:12.720
Every year at the Night Banquet,

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:15.399
the Villa Master brings out rare treasures

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:16.440
for everyone to admire.

00:11:16.559 --> 00:11:19.879
I wonder what treasure will be revealed tonight.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:22.799
Naturally, it is Baixiao Villa's...

00:11:23.919 --> 00:11:25.480
Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:26.639
Thou...

00:11:27.399 --> 00:11:28.879
The Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure!

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:31.080
It's the Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure.

00:11:35.279 --> 00:11:36.679
What is the Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure?

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:40.559
The Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure is a peerless treasure of the former dynasty.

00:11:41.240 --> 00:11:43.080
Whoever possesses it can rule the world.

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:44.799
For decades,

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:46.240
major sects in the Jianghu

00:11:46.440 --> 00:11:47.559
and various factions in the Imperial Court

00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:49.000
in order to obtain the secret treasure,

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:50.720
have stirred up a storm of bloodshed.

00:11:51.559 --> 00:11:53.240
But what exactly this Thousand-Mechanism Secret Treasure is,

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:54.679
remains unknown to this day.

00:11:55.759 --> 00:11:56.440
Come, everyone.

00:11:57.399 --> 00:11:57.879
Please.

00:11:58.279 --> 00:11:58.960
Please, please.

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:04.440
Careful.